  "text": "For each of the 128 electrodes, all the surrounding electrodes within a distance of 60 mm were calculated using the Fieldtrip toolbox [CITATION_1] , resulting in 128 clusters (median ¼ 20 electrodes per cluster, min ¼ 8, max ¼ 23). Two-way classification was performed using each of these clusters and classification accuracy was averaged across participants.",
